-- BEA says Oracle bid undervalues BEA
-- 
-- Fri Oct 12, 2007 1:33pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/10/12/us-bea-oracle-response-idUSWNAS624120071012

 

 LOS ANGELES  (Reuters) - Business software maker BEA Systems Inc BEAS.O said on Friday that its board had concluded that a $17 per share unsolicited takeover bid from Oracle Corp ORCL.O "significantly under-values BEA." 

